She turned it into something refined.

2059
01:34:51,211 --> 01:34:53,040
She made a unique dish.

2060
01:34:53,041 --> 01:34:54,941
On top of that, it was expensive in the beginning.

2061
01:34:55,141 --> 01:34:56,911
It was around 28 dollars.

2062
01:34:57,281 --> 01:35:00,451
(The Star In My Heart prepared the most expensive dish to share.)

2063
01:35:00,551 --> 01:35:02,821
Try this. It's really good.

2064
01:35:03,821 --> 01:35:05,350
I'm serious. Try it.

2065
01:35:05,351 --> 01:35:07,360
- We also ordered that.
- This is it.

2066
01:35:07,361 --> 01:35:08,420
There are only 20 supplies.

2067
01:35:08,421 --> 01:35:10,261
- We definitely have to try it.
- This one?

2068
01:35:10,591 --> 01:35:11,861
Twenty limited supplies.

2069
01:35:11,991 --> 01:35:13,231
What's this?

2070
01:35:13,331 --> 01:35:14,760
- This one?
- You can get it there.

2071
01:35:14,761 --> 01:35:16,931
- The Star In My Heart.
- Twenty limited supplies.

2072
01:35:17,031 --> 01:35:18,070
- Really?
- Yes.

2073
01:35:18,071 --> 01:35:19,100
How much is it?

2074
01:35:19,101 --> 01:35:21,670
We had many customers who came because...

2075
01:35:21,671 --> 01:35:24,270
- they saw other people eating it.
- Right.

2076
01:35:24,271 --> 01:35:26,011
That was part of our strategy.

2077
01:35:26,211 --> 01:35:28,610
We intentionally created a dish that looked substantial.

2078
01:35:28,611 --> 01:35:30,180
We also provided a lot on the side.

2079
01:35:30,181 --> 01:35:32,581
(Seasoned bean sprouts and potato salad)

2080
01:35:32,751 --> 01:35:34,581
It worked as a form of promotion.

2081
01:35:35,021 --> 01:35:36,751
(Checking the restaurant menu)

2082
01:35:36,881 --> 01:35:39,421
(Eyes fixed)

2083
01:35:39,451 --> 01:35:42,291
(Eyes fixed)

2084
01:35:42,721 --> 01:35:45,331
She knows how to play the game.

2085
01:35:45,931 --> 01:35:48,061
Even in a situation where everything was restricted,

2086
01:35:48,661 --> 01:35:52,100
I made sure that...

2087
01:35:52,101 --> 01:35:53,301
the value was justified.

2088
01:35:53,771 --> 01:35:55,901
People calling me a business genius...

2089
01:35:56,971 --> 01:35:58,311
I'll stop here.

2090
01:36:00,941 --> 01:36:03,111
- This is crazy.
- I know, but we survived.

2091
01:36:03,181 --> 01:36:05,011
Jae Beom, we survived, so we're safe.

2092
01:36:05,381 --> 01:36:07,281
I've been on survival shows before.

2093
01:36:15,621 --> 01:36:18,791
This cancels the survival...

2094
01:36:19,491 --> 01:36:20,561
of The Star In My Heart.

2095
01:36:24,001 --> 01:36:27,071
- What?
- That's ruthless.

2096
01:36:27,701 --> 01:36:29,601
- It's canceled?
- That's so harsh.

2097
01:36:30,971 --> 01:36:32,041
- What?
- Gosh.

2098
01:36:32,271 --> 01:36:33,471
Why was it canceled?

2099
01:36:35,111 --> 01:36:37,411
Are they doing it on purpose to make it entertaining?

2100
01:36:41,751 --> 01:36:44,421
Let's be honest. This is ridiculous.

2101
01:36:46,911 --> 01:36:48,821
(The competition is reset.)

2102
01:36:49,181 --> 01:36:50,751
(We can't sell it like this.)

2103
01:36:50,851 --> 01:36:52,691
(A ruthless, unpredictable real-world battle of business)

2104
01:36:53,391 --> 01:36:55,721
(We're in trouble. It's a race against time.)

2105
01:36:56,591 --> 01:36:57,990
(They must've waited for a long time.)

2106
01:36:57,991 --> 01:36:59,230
(It's a signal to serve them fast.)

2107
01:36:59,231 --> 01:37:02,361
(The first 1-star review appears.)

2108
01:37:03,501 --> 01:37:06,101
(That was a moment of total panic.)

2109
01:37:06,571 --> 01:37:08,170
Let's see who wins.

2110
01:37:08,171 --> 01:37:10,811
(Will it be rising newcomers...)

2111
01:37:10,841 --> 01:37:12,270
(or veterans fighting for survival?)

2112
01:37:12,271 --> 01:37:13,940
(Which restaurant recorded the lowest sales?)

2113
01:37:13,941 --> 01:37:15,211
(It damages my sense of pride.)

2114
01:37:15,341 --> 01:37:16,540
(I'll give everything I've got.)

2115
01:37:16,541 --> 01:37:18,181
(You think I can't make 1,000 dollars?)

2116
01:37:18,311 --> 01:37:22,521
(In an unpredictable real-world business,)

2117
01:37:22,951 --> 01:37:24,951
(be the first to survive.)

2118
01:37:25,451 --> 01:37:27,720
(The dinner sales begin.)

2119
01:37:27,721 --> 01:37:29,190
(I'm most curious about who will walk in.)

2120
01:37:29,191 --> 01:37:30,930
- The door to Street Arena...
- They are coming.

2121
01:37:30,931 --> 01:37:32,061
is opening.

2122
01:37:33,661 --> 01:37:34,831
(All of them are families.)

2123
01:37:35,401 --> 01:37:36,961
(All of them are children.)

2124
01:37:37,231 --> 01:37:39,000
(This changes everything.)

2125
01:37:39,001 --> 01:37:40,670
(Things are different from how they were at lunch.)

2126
01:37:40,671 --> 01:37:44,771
(Mom, I want some too.)

